However, normally you&#39;d create the scriptblock as a literal, either as a variable

```
$scriptblock = {
    if ( 1 -ne 2 ) {
        Write-Host &#39;Hello&#39;
    } else {
        Write-Host &#39;GoodBye&#39;
    }
}
Invoke-Command -ScriptBlock $scriptblock
